org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives

Class ObjectiveComparatorHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.ObjectiveComparatorHelper

  • public class ObjectiveComparatorHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible to compare and sort fitness values. TrajectoryFitness instances can be added to an instance of this class, that it can sort them.

      • compare

        public int compare(Fitness o1,
          Fitness o2)
        Compares two fitnesses based on hierarchical dominance. Returns -1 if the second parameter o2 is a better solution (o2 dominates o1), 1 if the first parameter o1 is better (o1 dominates o2) and returns 0 if they are non-dominating each other.
